Class MathStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • mathoscore.Data.Stack.Stack<java.lang.Integer>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStack<java.lang.Integer>

    public class MathStack
extends Stack<java.lang.Integer>
    A stack that can only contain integers. This is an extension of Stack class. All methods have the time complexity of O(1).
    Version:
    2015.02.06
